view.name: Average Salary by Job Classification
view.description:
This Dataset indicates average salary by position title and grade for full-time regular employees. Data excludes elected, appointed, non-merit and temporary employees. Underfilled positions are also excluded from the dataset.
Update Frequency : Annually

columns.name: Position Title
columns.description: The duties and responsibilities which make up the work performed by an employee.

columns.name: Position Class Code
columns.description: A subdivision of an occupational class consisting of positions similar as to specialized line of work and qualification requirements.

columns.name: Grade
columns.description: Numerical designation which identifies the range of difficulty and responsibility, and level of qualification requirements within respectice position titles.

columns.name: Average of Base Salary
columns.description: Average Salary for full-time employees within respective grade and position title.

columns.name: Number of Employees
columns.description: Total Number of Employees within respective grade and position title.
